free reserve space

tune2fs -m 0 /dev/sdb1


update time

ntpdate time1.google.com
replace the "0-3.centos.pool.ntp.org" or other NTP server with "time1-4.google.com" line by line.



you can install oracle or openjdk java by renaming it to  jdk-16.0.1-linux-x64.tar.gz or
 jdk-16.0.1-linux-i586.tar.gz and then use pat's java slackbuild to install it. make sure
 you copy the profile files to /etc/profile to make sure the system find the path
